---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'

const lastUpdated = 'May 2026'
const contactEmail = 'privacy@unionwith.app'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Union's privacy policy: what we collect, how we use it, your rights."
>
  <article class="prose-union">
    <h1 class="font-prayer text-5xl text-union-charcoal">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-union-secondary">
      Last updated: {lastUpdated}
    </p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      At Union (&ldquo;we&rdquo;, &ldquo;our&rdquo;, or &ldquo;us&rdquo;), we care about your privacy and aim to keep
      data collection simple, transparent, and minimal.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it,
      and your choices when using the Union app and related services
      (&ldquo;Services&rdquo;).
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Information We Collect
    </h2>

    <h3 class="mt-6 font-prayer text-2xl text-union-charcoal">
      Account Information
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      When you create an account, we may collect:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <li>Your email address</li>
      <li>Authentication information used to sign you in securely</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-6 font-prayer text-2xl text-union-charcoal">
      Usage Information
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We may collect limited information about how you use the app, including:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <li>App interactions and feature usage</li>
      <li>Device type and app version</li>
      <li>Diagnostic and crash information</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-6 font-prayer text-2xl text-union-charcoal">
      Content You Create
    </h3>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      If you use journaling, prayer, reflections, notes, or other personal
      features within Union, the content you create may be stored securely to
      provide the service to you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      How We Use Information
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">We use information to:</p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <li>Provide and improve the app</li>
      <li>Authenticate and secure your account</li>
      <li>Personalise your experience</li>
      <li>Maintain app performance and reliability</li>
      <li>Respond to support requests</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We do not sell your personal information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Data Storage &amp; Security
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your
      information from unauthorised access, loss, misuse, or disclosure.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      No online service can guarantee absolute security, but we work to keep
      your data protected and secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Your Rights
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Depending on your location, you may have rights to:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent where applicable</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      To make a privacy request, contact us at:
      <a class="text-union-gold underline" href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Data Retention
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We retain information only for as long as necessary to provide the
      Services, comply with legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce
      our agreements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Third-Party Services
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We use trusted service providers to help operate, maintain, and improve
      Union.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      These providers only process information necessary to provide their
      services to us.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Changes to This Policy
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make material
      changes, we will update the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date above.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 font-prayer text-3xl text-union-charcoal">
      Contact
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data,
      contact:
      <a class="text-union-gold underline" href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
